My name is Duncan Leckie and I am a Bristol based Clinical Hypnotherapist and a Registered Nurse.  Solution Focused Hypnotherapy uses practical, modern and well-researched strategies to help people make significant, positive changes in their lives in a relatively short period of time.

With Solution Focused Hypnotherapy, we look at what the client would like to achieve (the solution) rather than at whatever prompted them to visit us (the problem).

In essence the approach focuses on the present and future and not on the past. The Hypnotherapist asks the client to consider their preferred future, for instance, what would be better if the problem had improved? What would have changed? This enables the client’s possible solutions to become more obvious and gives the client a goal to work towards.

Hypnosis itself reduces anxiety and this is done very simply through relaxation and visualisation, allowing the client to focus on the positive aspects of their life, encouraging a shift in perspective.

I see my clients in central Bristol at:

19 Lower Redland Road, Bristol, BS6 6TB and also The Bedminster Family Practice, Regent Rd, Bristol, BS3 4AT

I am also able to see clients who are unable to leave their home to see me or anywhere in the world via Skype.

Depuis toujours, je suis une personne très sensible, j’ai constamment ressenti le besoin d’aider les gens. J’aime voir un sourire sur des visages.

À l’âge de 16 ans je commence à pratiquer la méditation régulièrement. Je m’intéresse dans le même temps à de nombreuses techniques et outils pour trouver mon chemin vers ma paix intérieure, mon bonheur et l’équilibre dans mon quotidien.
Tout ce que j’ai appris à maîtriser durant ces années m’a permis de changer da vie. De passer d’une personne stressée au quotidien, hypersensible et bouffée par le regard des gens. Qui avait peur de l’abandon et de finir seul.
